{
  "texts": [
    "The accuracy and results of JSON formatting of the responses are included in S4 Section.",
    "ChatGPT had an excellent True Negative Rate-over 96% for MMSE and 100% for CDR in double-reviewed notes (Table 4).",
    "Both results had high recall (sensitivity), reaching 89.7% for MMSE (macro-recall) and 91.3% for CDR (macro-recall).",
    "MMSE was more frequently mentioned in the notes and ChatGPT's macro precision (PPV) was 82.7%.",
    "CDR, on the other hand, was less frequent, and we observed that ChatGPT hallucinates (factitiously generates) results occasionally leading to a macro precision of only 57.5%."
  ]
}